title: Joseline Hernandez interview
itunes:title: Joseline Hernandez interview
description:
Today on the show we had the Puerto Rican princess Joseline Hernandez where she spoke about her Cabaret, getting back on Love and Hip- Hop, and being happy in her relationship. Moreover, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a rapper who told on himself for a triple homicide and after opened up the phone lines to see what our listeners thought about Loni Love's comments on Black men cheating.
